blueprint.label: Belts
blueprint.description:
In early game, use an "upgrade planner" to change all blue belts to red and all asm3 to asm2.

When blue belts and asm3 are available, REMOVE the asm2 and re-place the blueprint WITHOUT shift-click.  That will show what red belts need to be changed back to blue.  When the blueprint places without any conflict, all is good.  The construction station will fetch the required items.
